descp2: A string, one of `channels_last` (default) or `channels_first`. The ordering of the dimensions in the inputs.`channels_last` corresponds to inputs with shape`(batch, length, channels)` while `channels_first` corresponds to inputs with shape `(batch, channels, length)`.
